Limitations (By Design)

ğŸ§© No complex parsing â€” nested expressions are fragile

ğŸ’¥ Limited error handling â€” expect cryptic messages

ğŸŒ€ Dynamic everything â€” no type safety whatsoever

ğŸ§± OOP quirks â€” expression evaluation in methods may not behave as expected

âš™ï¸ Eval-based arithmetic â€” runs in a sandbox, but still limited


These arenâ€™t bugs â€” theyâ€™re Ceronaâ€™s identity.


